name: MeinaMix
description:
MeinaMix objective is to be able to do good art with little prompting.
I created a discord server where you can post images that you generated, discuss prompt and/or ask for help. https://discord.gg/meinaverse

I also have a ko-fi and Patreon page where you can support me or buy me a coffee <3 , it will be very much appreciated:
https://ko-fi.com/meina and https://www.patreon.com/MeinaMix

MeinaMix is officially hosted for online generation in
- SeaArt
- Sinkin.ai
- Magespace
- Tensor
- Dazzleai

MeinaMix and the other of Meinas will ALWAYS be FREE.

Recommendations of use:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Enable Quantization in K samplers.

Hires.fix is needed for prompts where the character is far away in order to make decent images, it drastically improve the quality of face and eyes!
---------------------------------------------
Recommended parameters:
Sampler: Euler a: 40 to 60 steps.
Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras: 30 to 60 steps.
Sampler: DPM++ 2M Karras: 20 to 60 steps.
CFG Scale: 4 to 11.
Resolutions: 512x768, 512x1024 for Portrait!
Resolutions: 768x512, 1024x512, 1536x512 for Landscape!
Hires.fix: R-ESRGAN 4x+Anime6b, with 15 steps at 0.4 denoising.
Clip Skip: 2.
Negatives: ' (worst quality, low quality:1.4), (zombie, sketch, interlocked fingers, comic), '
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

In the merged models list: MeinaMix V1~6, MeinaPastel V3~5, MeinaHentai V2~3, Night Sky YOZORA Style Model, PastelMix and Facebomb, i do not have the exact recipe because i did multiple mixings using block weighted merges with multiple settings and kept the better version of each merge.

modelVersions.name: Meina V6
modelVersions.description:
This version aims to retain the half realistic feel that MeinaMix have, while improving the capabilities of doing 2d and not realistic art.

Recommendations:

Euler a: 20 to 50 steps. OR DDIM: 20 to 50 steps.
CFG Scale between 5 to 9.
Resolutions of 512x768 or 768x512.
( it may be capable of doing 768x432 which is 16:9 but i've not tested).
Hires. fix: None or R-ESRGAN 4x, 10 Hires step, 0,3 to 0,6 Denoising.
Clip Skip 2.

The prompt can be simple or long, it will do fine without the meta tags. ( most of the samples do have meta tags because they're not mine. )

Negatives: ' (worst quality, low quality:1.4), [ng_deepnegative_v1_75t], (pale skin), '. ( pale skin is not needed but every now and then i would get very pale skin tone in the generations that had white hair )

As of right now, this was my favorite model to test, so i hope you guys enjoy it aswell!

modelVersions.name: Meina V5.1
modelVersions.description:
Some improvements over V5, mostly over the background and some details in the generation and in the light.

All of the images were generated using Clip Skip 2.

In negatives: ' (worst quality, low quality:1.4), ' OR ' (worst quality, low quality:1.4), (malformed hands:1.4),(poorly drawn hands:1.4),(mutated fingers:1.4),(extra limbs:1.35),(poorly drawn face:1.4), '

Doing smaller negative will help keep the creativity of the model, the longer negative will prevent it from that in exchange of a higher chance of getting good quality images in lower generations!

modelVersions.name: Meina V5
modelVersions.description:
( This is the baked VAE version )
This is more very versatile version of Meina, it can do 2.5d, anime and near realistic!

This version is much much much more capable of making NSFW images, tho is wasn't what i was aiming at. ( last sample images )

The sample images had these settings:

R-ESRGAN 4x+Anime6B upscaled by 2x at 15 steps and 0,6 Denoising.

Base res: 512x768 / 768x512.

Clip skip 1.

Recommended Neg Prompt:

' (worst quality, low quality:1.4), (malformed hands:1.4),(poorly drawn hands:1.4),(mutated fingers:1.4),(extra limbs:1.35),(poorly drawn face:1.4), '

Now a bit of Lore:

It's a mix of Meina V3, with V4 and V4.1.
And it kept a little bit of each of them, i was focusing mostly in the hands but i liked the images that this version was capable of doing!

My focus in the V3 was to be 2.5d, V4 was to be anime like, now V5 is good at both!!

If you've read up to here: Thank you very much for giving a chance to my model! and also Thank you for everyone who have been following every update and posting pictures, i love seeing the amazing results you guys make which gives me more motivation to keep trying to improve!

Not even joking, this one took atleast 200 changes in the blocks and mixing %... >.>

modelVersions.name: Meina V4.1
modelVersions.description:
This is the first oficial release of the V4 as the 4.0 was released while it was still in beta. For the tests of the 4.1 i made all of the sample images using:

  • In the negative prompt: ' (worst quality, low quality:1.4), (malformed hands:1.4),(poorly drawn hands:1.4),(mutated fingers:1.4),(extra limbs:1.35),(poorly drawn face:1.4), '

  • R-ESRGAN 4x+ with 10 steps and 0.6 denoising.

  • Clip Skip 1.

    So i strongly recommend you try those yourself too!!

    As for the improvements of 4.1 over 4.0:

  • No longer have the problem of most of the bodies looking too skinny or too fit.

  • Improved the hands!! ( long prompt still have a high chance of having messy hands )

  • The chances of generating a good image is higher than previous versions.

  • It handles horizontal and vertical generations!

  • Generating Hard NSFW is now harder.

  • But its still capable of generating NSFW images.

I'm looking forward to see the images everyone can generate using V4.1!!

( i'll try to make the version without VAE, but in case you have invokeAI there is an option to replace the VAE that is baked into a model to another VAE )

modelVersions.name: Meina V4
modelVersions.description:
This is to a certain point a beta version. If theres anything wrong then i'll update it as soon as possible.
I will be publishing more samples later on, together with the version that doesn't have VAE baked in.

  • This version makes more illustration like images.

  • The hand generation is better than 3.0 in avarage.

  • It tends to make bodies overly skinny/fit or muscular. ( thats a pro and con ) -> samples included.

  • Better poses and more versatility.

  • As per request, now V4 will have a version without VAE ( will be uploaded within 24h).

-- Things still needed to work on

  • make the hand generation chance be higher chance of making good hands without the need of much finetuning in order to fix the fingers.

  • Some things like Eye glow i feel like it was better in 3.0, so i'll try to add it back in the 4.0+.

  • In the tests, the upscaler i often use ( R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B ) broke the generation of hands more often than not, but lowering its value to lower than .50 seens to help in some cases.

  • It tends to make bodies skinny/fit or muscular. ( thats a pro and con ) -> Samples included.
